node.text: Epic and Dramatic skie dear bro 🖤🖤🖤🖤✨

Non-stop Lightning
Southern Islands
Singapore
Day 28 / 56
Covid-19 Circuit Breaker
5.02 am, 4 May 2020
Wow! I need to get an Olympus

@zanthrea 🤣 No lah. Just use my Olympus camera to capture the Long Exposure. It is Live Composite mode that can capture lightning, fireworks, astrophotography, Star & Light trails for very more than 3 hours long exposure without over expose the photo.
@zanthrea It can go beyond 3 hours with portable power bank to charge the camera battery & let the camera capture the light.
How did you capture this? Video freeze?
@isawthelight2 Thank you very much! Lightning season 🙏😉
Epic and Dramatic skie dear bro 🖤🖤🖤🖤✨
